Additional Terms — Educational Use

The pedagogical parameters (q=17, n=8, k=2) and all worked examples contained
in these notebooks are provided for educational purposes. They are intentionally
simplified and must not be used as the basis for any production cryptographic
system. For production use, refer to the official NIST FIPS 203 standard:
https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.FIPS.203
